sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Server
    participant PHP
    participant MySQL
    participant Game Engine
    
    Client->>Server: HTTP GET /index.php
    Server->>PHP: Process Request
    PHP->>PHP: Session Check
    
    alt Not Authenticated
        PHP-->>Client: Login Form
        Client->>Server: POST Credentials
        Server->>PHP: Validate
        PHP->>MySQL: Check User
        MySQL-->>PHP: User Data
        PHP->>PHP: Create Session
        PHP-->>Client: Game Interface
    else Authenticated
        PHP->>Game Engine: Load State
        Game Engine->>MySQL: Query Data
        MySQL-->>Game Engine: Game State
        Game Engine-->>PHP: Rendered View
        PHP-->>Client: Game HTML
    end
    
    Note over Client,Server: Continuous Polling
    loop Every 2 seconds
        Client->>Server: AJAX Check Updates
        Server->>PHP: Process
        PHP->>Game Engine: Check Changes
        Game Engine-->>PHP: Updates
        PHP-->>Client: JSON Response
    end